    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget-Friendly Project Car \u2014 Priced to Move! \ud83d\udd27\n\nLooking for an affordable entry point or a hands-on project? This vehicle is priced accordingly for its condition \u2014 it has seen better days and will require some meaningful repairs and attention to get it back in great shape. There are noticeable mechanical and cosmetic issues, so this one is best suited for a mechanically savvy buyer, a DIY enthusiast, or someone looking for parts. The price reflects the condition honestly \u2014 what you see is what you get, and there's real potential here for the right person willing to put in the work!",
